        "message": "=<p>Dear {{ $json.patient_name }},</p><p>Thank you for completing your pre-visit medical intake form. This email confirms that we have received your submission.</p><p>Your healthcare provider will review the information you submitted before your appointment. Please note this message does not contain any medical advice.</p><p>If your symptoms worsen or you experience an emergency, please contact your local emergency services immediately.</p><p>Kind regards,<br/>The Care Team</p>",
